  <brief_title>Examine National Characteristics &amp; Outcome Measures of GERD Patients Using the PPI Acid Suppression Symptom (PASS) Test for Response</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Cluster-Randomized Study to Examine National Characteristics and Outcome Measures of GERD Patients Utilizing the PPI Acid Suppression Symptom (PASS) Test for Response [EncomPASS].</official_title>
