  </study_design_info>
  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>To compare the improvement in burden of overall GERD symptoms after 4 weeks of treatment with Esomeprazole verses maintenance of current therapy in subjects with persistent GERD symptoms.</measure>
  </primary_outcome>
  <secondary_outcome>
    <measure>To examine the relationship of the severity and frequency of GERD symptoms to treatment, at national, and regional levels.</measure>
  </secondary_outcome>
